  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7627881">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7627881/" class="title-link">读《吕氏春秋》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7627881"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/42390148/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u42390148-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/42390148/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">三千</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-10-16"
      class="main-meta">2015-10-16 09:23:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7627881_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《吕氏春秋》现在多认为属于子部，以前也有将之归入史部的，这都是因为题中的“春秋”二字。史以陈事实，子以明义理。《吕氏春秋》分为十二纪、八览、六论，其中八览、六论都是以一个道理开头，然后列举数事以证之，可见其是以义理为主。十二纪则没有这么严格的模式，但论义理...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7627881_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7627881_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2818612">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2818612/" class="title-link">略评</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2818612"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/20174382/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/20174382/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">dandang</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-04"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-04 11:39:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2818612_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  似乎记得＜吕氏春秋集解＞前言谈到，高诱认为其书易于诸子而大出其右，因而寻罗而为之做注．还记得在书店里翻过一本三联的书，说它是兼容并包的杂家，并不掩赞誉之辞，然我读过后．除了其编年的写法和每篇以天文、历数、阴阳、礼仪、祭嗣、农耕为开篇的写法令为称道外，其他内...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2818612/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2818612_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2818612_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





